215
00:13:14.584 --> 00:13:15.585
Hakim Hwang.

216
00:13:40.193 --> 00:13:41.194
Mahkamah dengan ini memerintahkan

217
00:13:41.611 --> 00:13:43.029
Defendan Lee Bong-seok

218
00:13:43.279 --> 00:13:46.407
